text:
@lazarljubenovic did you mean "vast minority"?

As mentioned, [`ng-repeat`](https://docs.angularjs.org/api/ng/directive/ngRepeat) is from [AngularJS](https://github.com/angular/angular.js), not Angular (this repo) where `*ngFor` is used. 

Also please note that [AngularJS has reached LTS](https://blog.angular.io/stable-angularjs-and-long-term-support-7e077635ee9c) and is no longer being modified other than for security issues or major breaking changes to browser or jQuery support.
